com.ephesoft.dcma.util.logger

Interface EphesoftLogger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EphesoftLoggerImpl

    public interface EphesoftLogger
    EphesoftLogger a wrapper of org.apache.log4j.Logger for logging info, errors and other logging level log. statements.
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft
